<topic id='business_definition_adult_mental_health_care_cluster.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Adult Mental Health Care Cluster - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_adult_mental_health_care_cluster">Adult Mental Health Care Cluster</xref>
 is a type of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_cluster">CARE CLUSTER</xref>
 for adult 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_adult_mental_health_care_cluster">Adult Mental Health Care Cluster</xref>
 is part of a currency developed to support the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_tariff_payment_system">National Tariff Payment System</xref>
 for 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_mental_health_service">Mental Health Services</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_adult_mental_health_care_cluster">Adult Mental Health Care Clusters</xref>
 are 21 groupings of Mental Health 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 based on their characteristics, and are a way of classifying individuals utilising 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_mental_health_service">Mental Health Services</xref>
 that forms the basis for payment.        </p>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_adult_mental_health_care_cluster">Adult Mental Health Care Cluster</xref>
 is assigned using a decision tree or algorithm based on the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_person_score">PERSON SCORE</xref>
 from the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_adult_mental_health_clustering_tool">Adult Mental Health Clustering Tool</xref>
 undertaken by a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
 for the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
This is done by first assigning the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 to one of three 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_mental_health_care_cluster_super_class">Mental Health Care Cluster Super Classes</xref>, to narrow down the number of possible 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_adult_mental_health_care_cluster">Adult Mental Health Care Clusters</xref>
 which are applicable to the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 condition. The 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 is then assigned to the most appropriate of this sub-set of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_adult_mental_health_care_cluster">Adult Mental Health Care Clusters</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
Further information relating to the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_adult_mental_health_clustering_tool">Adult Mental Health Clustering Tool</xref>
 and 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_adult_mental_health_care_cluster">Adult Mental Health Care Clusters</xref>
 is available from the gov.uk website at: 
              <xref href="https://improvement.nhs.uk/resources/national-tariff/"
               scope="external"
               format="html">The NHS payment system: documents and guidance</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
